## Plan Management

Plans live in `plans/` at the project root (git-tracked):

```
plans/
  functional/draft/       New feature ideas
  functional/approved/    Business-approved features
  implementation/draft/   Technical design in progress
  implementation/approved/ Technical design approved
  todo/                   Ready for execution (Iron Loop injected)
  in_progress/            Currently being worked on
  review/                 Awaiting review
  done/                   Completed
```

| Command | Action |
|---------|--------|
| `ctoc` | Show status |
| `ctoc plan new "title"` | Create functional plan |
| `ctoc plan status` | Show plan dashboard |
| `ctoc plan approve <id>` | Approve a plan |

